# 🎬 Movie Watchlist

A simple and stylish web app to manage your personal movie watchlist. You can search for movies, add them to your list, and keep track of what you want to watch—all in one place.


---

## 📌 Features

- 🔍 Search for movies using the OMDb API
- ➕ Add and remove movies from your watchlist
- 💾 Saves your list using localStorage
- 📱 Responsive layout that works on all devices

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/mayurathod14/Movie-Watchlist.git
cd Movie-Watchlist


Movie-Watchlist/
│
├── index.html         # Main search page
├── watchlist.html     # Watchlist page
├── styles.css         # Styles for both pages
├── script.js          # JS for searching and adding movies
├── watchlist.js       # JS for managing the watchlist
├── images/            # Optional: posters or icons
└── README.md          # This file
